  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I fall in also in that category.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the way, let me tell you something like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Hungary, there was constantly about written in the paper about the Jewish question, [SPEAKING HUNGARIAN], I'm speaking Hungarian-- Jewish question.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were constantly busy what the Jewish question is, what to do with Jews now?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this Jewish question was then separated in three stages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, as the first is, who is a Jew?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In Hungary were a lot of assimilated Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So not everyone is a Jew who  goes on the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe his mother, his grandfather, his grandmother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they're first in the first stages in the first three stages.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First stage, a Jew is defined and so on, this and this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The second stage is more harsh than the third stage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have in front here, my book here, I have all this information that chronicles exactly about their laws, who's a Jew, the first  stage, the second stage, and the third stage.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But here, certainly, not every Jew falls in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Someone who doesn't keep his religion, someone who wasn't circumcised, some was his father wasn't Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in-- in Budapest, 300,000 Jews lived there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Among those more are assimilated, they're more-- more-- are not considered the Jews-- he is a Jew only by--- by relation, but he's not a Jew.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yes, these are stories which I can write and read books about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, but I fall in this category.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you have to go to there to-- to register this, to draft.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Number one, you're threatened that you're being killed, you're being in jailed, you're being this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And secondly, if your status is not registered, you cannot go to live no place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Another was, no one accepts you.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
